public String toString() {
        Iterator<E> i = iterator();
    	if (! i.hasNext())
    	    return ""[]"";
    
    	StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
    	sb.append('[');
    	for (;;) {
    	    E e = i.next();
    	    sb.append(e == this ? ""(this Collection)"" : e);
    	    if (! i.hasNext())
    		return sb.append(']').toString();
    	    sb.append("", "");
    	}
    }
